title: Salmon Snack Treats
product_description:
These irresistible training treats are made with real wild Alaskan salmon and wholesome ingredients. Perfect for training sessions, these small, soft treats are easy to break into smaller pieces and won't fill up your pet's stomach.

Perfect for:

  • Training sessions
  • Positive reinforcement
  • Rewarding good behavior
  • Dental health (helps clean teeth)
ingredients: Ingredients: Wild Alaskan Salmon, Organic Brown Rice Flour, Organic Pea Flour, Organic Sweet Potato, Organic Coconut Oil, Organic Flaxseed, Vitamins (Vitamin E Supplement, Niacin, Vitamin A Supplement, Thiamine Mononitrate, Pyridoxine Hydrochloride, Riboflavin, Vitamin D3 Supplement, Vitamin B12 Supplement, Folic Acid), Minerals (Zinc Sulfate, Ferrous Sulfate, Copper Sulfate, Manganese Sulfate, Calcium Iodate, Sodium Selenite), Mixed Tocopherols (preservative), Rosemary Extract.
